ygData.messageBody:
> Nice Stats:
>
> 16 AC
> +5 Str
> +5 STA
> -9 CHA (who cares? take it off when you sell)
>
> I have heard its on Ympe the Infernal (or some such
> thing) in Beholder Maze.
>
> Anyone know about what level he is?

Agreed, nice stats. No, I don't know what level he is, but I have seen many
early 20s characters running around with a ribcage (that may tell you
something). Personally, I don't wear any kind of armor unless it looks like
plate. It's just a peeve of mine, heh. But dark elves just look so cool in
plate (and hot damn our crotches are the BEST).

Dravith Vandre'i
